      <scopecontent id="aspace_e6957ec2e4df2c9b31773a8453ac519f">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of promotional material, correspondence, lease and license agreements, project records and memorabilia documenting the publication of <title render="italic">
               <part>The Chronicles of America</part>
            </title> and <title render="italic">
               <part>Chronicles of America Photoplays</part>
            </title> by the Yale University Press.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
